      "when_zapier_is_still_right": "Keep Zapier when the Gmail workflow is lightweight, low risk, and easy for a person to verify after the fact. It works well for a simple alert, a personal productivity step, or a short-term mailbox experiment where occasional polling delay, reply-driven duplicates, or manual attachment checks will not disrupt an important process.",
